 * Workbook architecture and dependency scanner.
 *
 * RESUMABLE CORE AUDIT
 * - Stops safely before Apps Script timeout
 * - Saves exact sheet/row progress
 * - Stores growing audit data in hidden Engine staging sheets
 * - Automatically resumes with a one-time trigger
 * - Writes final reports only after scanning completes
 *
 * CURRENT CAPABILITIES
 * - Formula dependency map
 * - Cross-sheet reference map
 * - IMPORTRANGE detection
 * - Named-range map
 * - Data-validation dependency map
 * - Conditional-formatting dependency map
 * - Source-of-truth architecture audit
 * - High-impact cell/range risk report
 * - Broken formula detection
 * - Selected-cell dependency inspector
 *
 * IMPORTANT
 * This version scans the spreadsheet itself.
 * Script source-code scanning will be added in
 * the next DependencyOS phase.
 *************************************************/


